<h2>Rules for staff profiles</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Must only be used in the main body of the page.</li>
	<li>The biography excerpt must not exceed 550 characters.</li>
	<li>If a biography excerpt exceeds 550 characters, and there is a user case to include all information, then a standalone biography page should be considered as an alternative.</li>
	<li>The profile image must be 200 &times; 200 pixels.</li>
	<li>Photographs must be headshots of the individual named in the card and of professional quality.</li>
	<li>The heading link and the full biography link must link to the same page.</li>
	<li>Contact information should be present if available.</li>
</ul>

